beginningReaders %>%
  select(., ReadingScore, LogRT) %>%
  ggplot(., aes(x = LogRT, y = ReadingScore)) +
  geom_point()+
  labs(x="Reading Times", y = "Reading Scores", title = "My Beginning Readers Scatterplot")
